title: World ranking of Faroe Islands ' national football team 1993 to 2019
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing FIFA World Ranking position, with a total of 27 data points. The chart has 8 significant trends.
The longest trend is extremely negative which exists from 2002 to 2007.
On the contrary, the next significant trend is moderately negative which exists from 1993 to 1996.
Differently, the next significant trend is moderately positive which exists from 1996 to 1999.
Additionally, the next significant trend is moderately positive which exists from 1999 to 2002.
Also, the next significant trend is slightly negative which exists from 2007 to 2010.
Differently, the next significant trend is extremely negative which exists from 2010 to 2013.
Conversely, the next significant trend is slightly positive which exists from 2013 to 2016.
Likewise, the next significant trend is extremely negative which exists from 2016 to 2019.
gold: In 2016 , the Faroe Island 's national football team , controlled by the Football Association of the Faroe Islands , reached its highest position in the FIFA World Ranking . The team took part in the qualifying for the UEFA European Championship 2016 . Out of the ten qualifying matches , the Faroe Island 's national football team won both matches against Greece .
